    "description": "《冰封之焰》官方QQ群：398937562<br>官方推荐加速器：UU 加速器，奇游加速器<br><br>《冰封之焰》是一款支持多人合作的探索冒险游戏，游戏的故事发生在一片远古的土地——阿尔卡纳。而世间的万物都诞生自冰灵焰，也终将回归于冰灵焰。生生不息，轮回往复。然而，无面者军团的出现彻底打破了平衡，大地被侵蚀殆尽，生命的轮回彻底崩坏……<br><br><strong>目前游戏支持超过4人的好友联机，或10人+的自设服务器联机。（最大联机人数视服务器质量决定）<br>未来将开放容纳更多人的生存模式官方服务器。</strong><br><br>在游戏中玩家将置身于一个地形复杂多变的开放世界，从空中浮岛、广阔沙漠到冰封大陆，你将能够自由地探索世界中的每一个角落。不过，这片土地中处处都潜藏着危机，你需要在恶劣环境、邪恶敌人甚至巨型怪物的威胁下努力奋战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拯救世界的命运</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1716898541\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/5d0ff81dea91d4a6ee21b84eb5d9a3b7.poster.avif?t=1716898541\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/5d0ff81dea91d4a6ee21b84eb5d9a3b7.webm?t=1716898541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/5d0ff81dea91d4a6ee21b84eb5d9a3b7.mp4?t=1716898541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>邪恶的无面者占据了冰堡，并将它们的爪牙伸向了阿卡纳的大地。随着时间的推移，它们的力量也在逐步增强，若再不加以阻止，这片仅存的世界也将陷入永冻的冰霜之中。现在，只有能够运用冰灵焰力量的骑士团才能够与之对抗，世界的命运现在就交由你们来决定了。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发掘亘古深埋的学识</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1716898541\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/66c330484fa5b3d60226361eac046f9b.poster.avif?t=1716898541\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/66c330484fa5b3d60226361eac046f9b.webm?t=1716898541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/66c330484fa5b3d60226361eac046f9b.mp4?t=1716898541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在远古时期人类的能工巧匠们曾创造出了大量的奇巧别致的物件，甚至一砖一瓦创造出了巍峨的城堡以及能够守护人类的石头巨人。然而时间将过去的一切掩埋在尘土之中，探寻古老的遗迹，发掘那些早已失落的学识，将其转化为对抗无面者军团的强大力量。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >集结盟友共同战斗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1716898541\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/39ccc04ec76056ecf2c62d5ab9ab7490.poster.avif?t=1716898541\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/39ccc04ec76056ecf2c62d5ab9ab7490.webm?t=1716898541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/39ccc04ec76056ecf2c62d5ab9ab7490.mp4?t=1716898541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>面对无面者强大的军团，虽然有冰灵焰的魔法力量能够助你一臂之力，但是孤军奋战终归难敌海量强敌。不妨召集你的好友加入战斗，以战士、法师、弓箭手三大职业配合强力天赋，哪怕是再强大的敌人也能够轻松应对。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造你的专属家园</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1716898541\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/c49571a17cb878f0587e182e78a72c44.poster.avif?t=1716898541\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/c49571a17cb878f0587e182e78a72c44.webm?t=1716898541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715400/extras/c49571a17cb878f0587e182e78a72c44.mp4?t=1716898541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在探索的途中不断发掘全新素材，利用各种不同的建筑材料亲手搭建一个能够保护你队伍的房屋甚至堡垒，从而避免受到来自这片诅咒之地恶劣环境的伤害。",
